original_title: 仮面ライダーW（ダブル）RETURNS 仮面ライダーアクセル
overview: While settling into married life with Akiko, Ryu is brought into a case  involving a woman named Katsuragi Aoi, a member of a pickpocketing ring with most of her teammates murdered from unknown masked vigilantes that Ryu fought as Accel. As the details of the case begin to unravel, Ryu is framed and Akiko believes that he may not be faithful to her. As the clock ticks down, Ryu must solve the case, clear his name, and save his marriage before everything comes to an explosive end!
title: Kamen Rider W Returns: Kamen Rider Accel
